query:
INSERT INTO monthly_gp_stats (gamePresenterId, month, year, attitude, mistakes, totalGames, createdAt, updatedAt)
SELECT id, 1, 2026, 4, 3, 1500, NOW(), NOW()
FROM game_presenters WHERE name LIKE '%Agnes Suvorov%'
ON DUPLICATE KEY UPDATE mistakes = 3, attitude = 4, totalGames = 1500;
